---
title: Crunchy Chocolate Peanut Butter Bars Serves 2 | with Corn Flakes
description: Cornflakes are the secret crunch to these easy peasy peanut butter bars! Mix, pour and chill and you'll have scrumptious peanut butter bars in under 30 min!

